fields.description:
I'm unable to access the Dashboard from 2 different macs that I use to do development. Yesterday it was working fine. PC access is fine but I'm building for iPhone right now so that doesn't help much :)

Error Message: An exception occurred in the script. Error name: TypeError. Error description: undefined. Error number: undefined. Error message: 'undefined' is not a function

OSX 10.6.8 Please advise
fields.summary: Unable to access dashboard on 2 different Macs

comments.body:
Hello Joe, 

can you please update to the latest Ti Studio? 

Best,

Mauro
Yep - it says no updates are available.

Joe,

BTW, can you please upload an screnshot of the message you are getting? 

TIA!
